\pard\nowidctlpar\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1 1. \tab Click the Start button on the taskbar.\par
2.\~\~\~Click All Programs.\par
3.\~\~\~From the expanded menu of programs and folders, click on the "Microsoft Silverlight" folder.\par
4.\~\~\~Click on the "Microsoft Silverlight" program shown in the "Microsoft Silverlight" folder to open the configuration tool.\par
